{"pid":"df99917886d2ca07a81e8c5f88a0dad275df9f05","tid":2348908,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"787d0f4b47bfc91d8b24c1cbafe0f8c9b9695ba2","tid":2348908,"uid":16326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"你能改變什麼？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱狗：挽回司法公正，建議區院引入陪審團<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2096511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2096511</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:16:04.000Z","msg":"好建議<br />\n但港共一定一棍打死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"0f04d9fb1dadc881ead9c7674b9e39b31d3ef7a9","tid":2348908,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:38:28.000Z","msg":"国安法：無需陪審團<br />\n熱狗：挽回司法公正，建議區院引入陪審團<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2096511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2096511</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰憂慮《国安法》下終審法院判決亦可被推翻<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192649</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭錦滿：死因庭不是尋求公義的地方，但區域法院可以。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2201932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2201932</a>"}}